name: Walking
about: Why it's a winner: You can walk anywhere, anytime. Use a treadmill or hit the streets. How to: If you're just starting to walk for fitness

name: Interval Training
about: Why it's a winner: Interval training boosts your fitness levels and burns more calories to help you lose weight.

name: Squats
about: Why it's a winner: Squats work several muscle groups -- your quadricephamstrings, and gluteals-- at the same time.

name: Lunges
about: Why it's a winner: Like squats, lunges work all the major muscles of your lower body. They can also improve your balance.

name: Push-Ups
about: Why it's a winner: Push-ups strengthen your chest, shoulders, triceps, and core muscles.How to: Facing down,

about: Start by lying on your back with your feet flat on the floor and your head resting in the palm of one hand
